&lt;h2 id="1-准备工作">1. 准备工作
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="11-系统要求">1.1 系统要求
&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>仅支持UEFI启动设备（包括虚拟机）&lt;/li>
&lt;li>不支持Legacy BIOS启动&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="12-所需材料">1.2 所需材料
&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Arch Linux ISO镜像&lt;/li>
&lt;li>实体机安装需要U盘（建议容量≥4GB）&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 id="13-注意事项">1.3 注意事项
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>❗ &lt;strong>重要警告&lt;/strong>：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>操作前请备份所有重要数据&lt;/li>
&lt;li>建议新手先在虚拟机中练习&lt;/li>
&lt;li>本教程默认使用清华镜像源加速下载&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="2-创建live环境">2. 创建Live环境
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="21-制作启动盘">2.1 制作启动盘
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># 使用dd命令写入镜像（Linux/Mac）&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">dd &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>archlinux.iso &lt;span class="nv">of&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/dev/sdX &lt;span class="nv">bs&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>4M &lt;span class="nv">status&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>progress
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="22-启动live系统">2.2 启动Live系统
&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>从U盘启动进入Arch Linux Live环境&lt;/li>
&lt;li>检查网络连接：&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ping archlinux.org
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="3-磁盘分区与格式化">3. 磁盘分区与格式化
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="31-分区方案">3.1 分区方案
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">cfdisk /dev/sda
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>推荐分区布局：&lt;/p>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th>挂载点&lt;/th>
&lt;th>大小&lt;/th>
&lt;th>类型&lt;/th>
&lt;th>文件系统&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>/boot/efi&lt;/td>
&lt;td>500M&lt;/td>
&lt;td>EFI System&lt;/td>
&lt;td>FAT32&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>/&lt;/td>
&lt;td>剩余空间&lt;/td>
&lt;td>Linux root&lt;/td>
&lt;td>Btrfs&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h3 id="32-格式化分区">3.2 格式化分区
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkfs.fat -F32 -n &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ARCH-EFI&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /dev/sda1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mkfs.btrfs -L &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;arch-root&amp;#34;&lt;/span> /dev/sda2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="4-btrfs子卷配置">4. Btrfs子卷配置
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="41-创建子卷">4.1 创建子卷
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mount /dev/sda2 /mnt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">btrfs subvolume create /mnt/@
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">btrfs subvolume create /mnt/@timeshift
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">umount /mnt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="42-优化挂载参数">4.2 优化挂载参数
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>根据硬件选择（完整参数见原教程）：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1"># SSD通用方案&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">mount -o &lt;span class="nv">subvol&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>@,compress&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>zstd:3,noatime,ssd /dev/sda2 /mnt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="5-系统安装">5. 系统安装
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="51-基础安装">5.1 基础安装
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacstrap /mnt base linux linux-firmware
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="52-生成fstab">5.2 生成fstab
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">genfstab -U /mnt &amp;gt;&amp;gt; /mnt/etc/fstab
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="6-系统配置">6. 系统配置
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="61-基础配置">6.1 基础配置
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">arch-chroot /mnt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">hwclock --systohc
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="62-本地化设置">6.2 本地化设置
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;LANG=zh_CN.UTF-8&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &amp;gt; /etc/locale.conf
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">echo&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;iUseArchBTW&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &amp;gt; /etc/hostname
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="7-引导配置">7. 引导配置
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="71-安装grub">7.1 安装GRUB
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grub-install --target&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>x86_64-efi --efi-directory&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/boot/efi
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="8-桌面环境安装">8. 桌面环境安装
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="81-安装gnome">8.1 安装GNOME
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">pacman -S xorg gnome gdm
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">systemctl &lt;span class="nb">enable&lt;/span> gdm
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="9-完成安装">9. 完成安装
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">exit&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">umount -R /mnt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">reboot
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>首次启动后建议：&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>创建Timeshift快照&lt;/li>
&lt;li>安装必要驱动&lt;/li>
&lt;li>配置用户环境&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>ArchLinux Plasma 6 开启Samba服务（文件共享）</title><link>https://blog.moieo.net/2025/04/24/220548/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Apr 2025 22:05:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.moieo.net/2025/04/24/220548/</guid><description>&lt;p>在 Plasma 6 中的 Dolphin 使用文件共享&lt;/p>
